This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image generation from freehand sketches. It could also belong to the Graphics (cs.GR) sub-category as it involves generating images from sketches. Additionally, the use of a generative adversarial network (GAN) suggests that it could belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Finally, the mention of a large-scale composite dataset suggests that it could also belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
